title: BitcoinMoses
author: BitcoinMoses
content: I want to know 'Why the Bitcoin.Org has Deleted the Bitcoin White Paper ?'Can any body tell me the truth nothing but the truth. Who is now running the Bitcoin.Org ?  Is the one known as BitcoinCobra or CobraBitcoin ?  I want the Bitcoin.Org to putback the Bitcoin White Paper online.  What is really happening to Bitcoin.Org ?  Is Craig Wright causing problems for Bitcoin.Org to publish the Bitcoin White Paper ?  If that is the case then why have'nt you ask me for legal help ?  Satoshi Nakamoto

comments.author: SquirrelJulietGarden
comments.body: Domain name updateSince 2020, Bitcoin.org and bitcointalk.org have no cross management and operations. Bitcoin.org after that belongs to Cobra only. Bitcointalk.org after that belongs to theymos only.If you need Bitcoin Core wallet software, not only Bitcoin White Paper, you can always download many versions from https://bitcoincore.org/en/download/ and get older versions at https://bitcoincore.org/en/releases/
